extends ../layout/layout

append css_content
  link(rel='stylesheet', href='/css/home.css')
block content
  .home-img-wrap
    .home-img-cover
    .home-img-content
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-6
            .home-img-phone
              .home-phone-show-wrap
                .home-phone-show
                  .clearfix.wx-box.wx-user
                    .wx-img
                    .wx-msg Hi
                  .clearfix.wx-box.wx-robot
                    .wx-img
                    .wx-msg 你好呀~ 有什么可以帮到你？
              form#robot-test-form
                input.form-control#robot-test-question(type='text')
          .col-md-6
            .clearfix
              .home-test-robot(href='javascript:{}') 点我试试
            h1.home-title 专业的私人美食助手 未来的餐饮服务入口
            .home-sub-title
              div “听说日本的怀石料理很有名，我想了解下。”
              div “我想吃天妇罗，哪家店做的好呢？”
              div 发条信息 全部搞定
            button.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.btn-try(data-toggle='modal', data-target='.bs-qrcode-modal') 立即体验
  .modal.fade.bs-qrcode-modal(tabindex="-1", role="dialog", aria-labelledby="mySmallModalLabel", aria-hidden="true")
    .modal-dialog.modal-sm
      .modal-content
        .modal-header
          button.close(type="button",data-dismiss="modal",aria-label="Close")
            span(aria-hidden="true") ×
          h4#mySmallModalLabel.modal-title 请用微信扫描二维码
            a.anchorjs-link(href="#mySmallModalLabel")
              span.anchorjs-icon
        .modal-body
          img.home-qrcode(src='/img/qrcode.jpg')
  .info-wrap
    .container
      .home-info
        .home-info-row.row
          .col-md-4
            .home-info-col
              .home-info-logo.logo-color-green
                i.glyphicon.glyphicon-stats
              .home-info-text 我们已拥有数千条日料小知识，了解全国近万家日料餐厅。
          .col-md-4
            .home-info-col
              .home-info-logo.logo-color-yellow
                i.glyphicon.glyphicon-tint
              .home-info-text 高大上的智能机器人栈栈，等你来勾搭。
          .col-md-4
            .home-info-col
              .home-info-logo.logo-color-red
                i.glyphicon.glyphicon-heart
              .home-info-text 最棒的你，做为日料吃货，怎能错过随身日料小助手。
  .home-feedback
    .container
      .home-feedback-title 听听日料吃货们怎么说
      #home-feedback.carousel.slide
        ol.carousel-indicators
          li.active(data-target="#home-feedback", data-slide-to="0")
          li(data-target="#home-feedback", data-slide-to="1")
          li(data-target="#home-feedback", data-slide-to="2")
        .carousel-inner
          .item.active
            .carousel-caption.clearfix
              .home-feedback-user.pull-left
                img(src='http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLBAgruxQ761LJI8tIN1zugjCrp5eR4iadXGulovmOUCznvJNDCe2Opgl93qwVaxgHdQvxcjn66qkEg/0')
              .home-feedback-user-text
                .home-feedback-user-content “在晚饭时间给我看这么好吃的日料，让不让人活了，换衣服，出门吃寿司去！”
                .home-feedback-user-name @唯唯安
          .item
            .carousel-caption.clearfix
              .home-feedback-user.pull-left
                img(src='http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/uPlnTpl7nOHgRc7mPXZaPD3Newt8UL2Llw2u39cetJrH5ArE7mcOFibEx4riaiauVmickmJZGGwI3FXzTzawxhXZAQ/0')
              .home-feedback-user-text
                .home-feedback-user-content “日料栈终将拯救吃货们的世界”
                .home-feedback-user-name @曹大俠是減肥計劃破壞
          .item
            .carousel-caption.clearfix
              .home-feedback-user.pull-left
                img(src='http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/gOsZsficuW87oqjP55WWY3QmdkD1CEdZXQpmDnNWxW11ibW1SWMWWDs1yexjZv75RqQVTRVbWvbjq39LDBtpfFmRzCuibUeTMLz/0')
              .home-feedback-user-text
                .home-feedback-user-content “小伙伴们，你们要不要吃的这么欢乐~”
                .home-feedback-user-name @YOKO胡
        a.left.carousel-control(href='#home-feedback', role="button", data-slide="prev")
          span.glyphicon.glyphicon-chevron-left(aria-hidden="true")
          span.sr-only Previous
        a.right.carousel-control(href='#home-feedback', role="button", data-slide="next")
          span.glyphicon.glyphicon-chevron-right(aria-hidden="true")
          span.sr-only Next
  .data-wrap
    .container
      .home-datas
        .row
          .col-md-3
            .panel.data-panel.data-panel-user.clearfix
              .data-icon-wrap
                i.glyphicon.glyphicon-user
              .data-content
                .data-content-val 4470
                .data-content-info 用户
          .col-md-3
            .panel.data-panel.data-panel-music.clearfix
              .data-icon-wrap
                i.glyphicon.glyphicon-question-sign
              .data-content
                .data-content-val 5285
                .data-content-info 提问
          .col-md-3
            .panel.data-panel.data-panel-headphones.clearfix
              .data-icon-wrap
                i.glyphicon.glyphicon-cloud
              .data-content
                .data-content-val 1834
                .data-content-info 知识
          .col-md-3
            .panel.data-panel.data-panel-cutlery.clearfix
              .data-icon-wrap
                i.glyphicon.glyphicon-cutlery
              .data-content
                .data-content-val 6260
                .data-content-info 餐厅
append js_content
  script(src='/lib/jquery-backstretch/jquery.backstretch.min.js')
  script(src='/js/home.js')